OL,3,CSouthern Water warn issues will
OL,4,Ccontinue in Hastings and St Leonards
OL,6,FSouthern Water is warning problems
OL,7,Fwith the mains supply will continue
OL,8,Ffor people in Hastings and St Leonards
OL,9,Fdespite homes being reconnected.
OL,11,FWater will be restored to the
OL,12,Fremaining 2,000 homes who've been
OL,13,Faffected by a burst water main since
OL,14,FFriday, with 30,000 households
OL,15,Freconnected by Tuesday morning.
OL,17,FDespite the pipe being fixed, the
OL,18,Fcompany is warning that properties
OL,19,Fwill experience low pressure by 'peak
OL,20,Fdemand'.
