OL,6,FThe firm said, "Peak demand is causing
OL,7,Flow pressure problems due to the
OL,8,Fgeography of the area and we therefore
OL,9,Fexpect customers to experience
OL,10,Fintermittent supplies as we build up
OL,11,Freservoir levels and increase water
OL,12,Fpressure.
OL,14,F"We're also dealing with a small burst
OL,15,Fin the Fairlight area as a result of
OL,16,Frestoring supply, which we have a team
OL,17,Fworking on right now.
