OL,4,Ccontinue in Hastings and St Leonards
OL,6,F"During peak demand times, customers
OL,7,Fare likely to still experience
OL,8,Ffluctuations in pressure.
OL,9,FUnderstandably, customers will be
OL,10,Fusing more water than usual as well
OL,11,Fand we're working hard to manage the
OL,12,Fdemand."
OL,14,FThe outage has caused a great deal of
OL,15,Ffrustration for business owners, with
OL,16,Fsome hotels having to collect seawater
OL,17,Fto flush their toilets.
