OL,6,FAll schools and colleges in the area
OL,7,Fopened as normal on Tuesday but three
OL,8,Fbottled water stations remains in
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,FSince the problems started, more than
OL,12,Fone million litres of bottled water
OL,13,Fhave been delivered to vulnerable
OL,14,Fcustomers, making it one of the
OL,15,Fbiggest bottled water operations ever
OL,16,Fhandled by Southern Water.
OL,18,FAround 400 employees of the company
OL,19,Fhave been involved in managing the
OL,20,Fincident, as well as contractor
OL,21,Fpartners.
