OL,6,FA fleet of 24 tankers have been
OL,7,Fdeployed to support those areas still
OL,8,Fwithout supply.
OL,10,FEast Sussex county councillor Godfrey
OL,11,FDaniel said the impact on businesses
OL,12,Fin Hastings would be "drastic".
OL,14,FSouthern Water said that the burst
OL,15,Fmain is in Keeper's Wood, near the
OL,16,FA21, "deep in woodland", which made it
OL,17,Fdifficult for crews and machinery to
OL,18,Freach it.
