OL,6,FThe company said they were "deeply
OL,7,Fsorry" for the loss of supply and they
OL,8,Fhad been working around the clock to
OL,9,Ffix the issue and help customers,
OL,10,Fespecially those who are vulnerable.
OL,12,FThey added, "If you are a vulnerable
OL,13,Fcustomer, or need access to water for
OL,14,Fmedical reasons, and have not received
OL,15,Fa water delivery or had yours stolen,
OL,16,Fplease call 0330 303 0368 to let us
OL,17,Fknow we need to help."
